Sentencas: Cation-doped CeO2 electrolyte has been evaluated in single-cell and short-stack tests in solid oxide fuel cell environments and applications.
Titulo: Properties and performance of cation-doped ceria electrolyte materials in solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: These results, along with conductivity measurements, indicate that an ionic transference number of similar to0.75 can be expected at 800degreesC. Single cells have shown a power density >350 mW/cm(2).
Titulo: Properties and performance of cation-doped ceria electrolyte materials in solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: Multicell stacks have demonstrated a peak performance of >100 mW/cm(2) at 700degreesC using metallic separators.
Titulo: Properties and performance of cation-doped ceria electrolyte materials in solid oxide fuel cell applications
